@startuml
title Cloudflare RealtimeKit Demo Main Flow

actor User
participant "React/Vite frontend" as Frontend
participant "Hono Worker API" as Worker
participant "Cloudflare RealtimeKit API" as RealtimeKit
participant "Workers Observability" as Observability

== Create meeting ==
User -> Frontend: Enter display name and optional title
Frontend -> Worker: POST /api/meetings
Worker -> RealtimeKit: Create meeting
RealtimeKit --> Worker: meetingId
Worker -> RealtimeKit: Add participant with preset
RealtimeKit --> Worker: participant auth token
Worker --> Frontend: meetingId, authToken
Frontend -> RealtimeKit: Initialize SDK with authToken
Frontend --> User: Render RtkMeeting

== Join meeting ==
User -> Frontend: Enter display name and meetingId
Frontend -> Worker: POST /api/meetings/{meetingId}/join
Worker -> RealtimeKit: Add participant with preset
RealtimeKit --> Worker: participant auth token
Worker --> Frontend: meetingId, authToken
Frontend -> RealtimeKit: Initialize SDK with authToken
Frontend --> User: Render RtkMeeting

== Webhook ==
RealtimeKit -> Worker: POST /api/realtimekit/webhook
Worker -> Observability: Structured event log
Worker --> RealtimeKit: 2xx accepted

@enduml
